meta.desc: Listen to SomaFm free internet radio in your GNOME desktop
meta.desc_long:
Listen to SomaFm free internet radio in your GNOME desktop

* Featues:
- 32+ Channels
- Volume slider
- Favorites menu
- Good sound quality
- Supports most gnome-shell versions
- Channel logos

* Requirements:
- Gstreamer and plugins:
You need to install 'gstreamer' and multimedia codecs/plugins for your distro.
